snippet.title: Madden 23 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
See how FieldSENSE in Madden NFL 23 changes everything. 

Available now: http://x.ea.com/73774

Watch the Madden 23 launch trailer featuring Justin Jefferson, Micah Parsons, Cordae, Hit-Boy, NickMercs, and Taylor Rooks. Providing the foundation for consistent, ultra-realistic gameplay, and only available on PlayStation®5 and Xbox Series X|S, the all-new FieldSENSE Gameplay System equips players with more control at all positions in every mode.
